---
layout: base.njk
bodyClass: home-page
title: vaemptîness - brain training
seo:
  title: "vaemptîness | Entrenamiento Mental y Mindfulness Barcelona"
  description: "Crea espacio mental. Entrenamiento cerebral basado en mindfulness y filosofía budista. Programas para adultos, equipos, adolescentes y niños en Barcelona."
  keywords: "entrenamiento mental Barcelona, mindfulness Barcelona, meditación Barcelona, psicología budista, reducir ansiedad, claridad mental, rumiación mental"
  ogImage: "/assets/images/og-home.jpg"
  ogType: "website"
---

<section class="hero">
  <!-- Circle stroke animation decoration -->
  <svg class="hero-circle-animation" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
    <circle
      cx="100"
      cy="100"
      r="95"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
    />
  </svg>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span class="hero-brand">{{ hero.title }}</span>
        <span class="hero-tagline">{{ hero.tagline }}</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Crea espacio mental,<br class="mobile-break"> libérate del ruido.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scroll-indicator" aria-label="Scroll down">
      <span class="scroll-text">Descubre más</span>
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M12 4L12 20M12 20L6 14M12 20L18 14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="learning-intro-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="learning-intro">
      <p class="intro-text">Un enfoque que fusiona teoría y práctica en cada experiencia, donde el aprendizaje sucede mientras lo vives.</p>
      <p class="quote-large">"No memorizas conceptos, <br class="desktop-break">los experimentas"</p>
      <a href="{{ '/aprendizaje-y-metodologia/' | url }}" class="button button-primary">Conocer más</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="principles-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="principles-grid">
      {% for principle in hero.principles %}
      <div class="principle-card">
        <!-- Progressive circle indicator -->
        <svg class="principle-circle" viewBox="0 0 60 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle
            cx="30"
            cy="30"
            r="26"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            {% if loop.index == 1 %}
            stroke-dasharray="163.4"
            stroke-dashoffset="98"
            {% elif loop.index == 2 %}
            stroke-dasharray="163.4"
            stroke-dashoffset="49"
            {% else %}
            stroke-dasharray="163.4"
            stroke-dashoffset="0"
            {% endif %}
          />
        </svg>

        <h2 class="principle-title">{{ principle.title }}</h2>
        <p class="principle-description">{{ principle.description }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="philosophy-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="philosophy-content">
      <p class="quote-emphasis">{{ hero.philosophy }}</p>
      <a href="{{ '/reset/' | url }}" class="button button-primary">Haz reset</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="programs-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Nuestros Programas</h2>

    <div class="programs-grid">
      {% for program in programs %}
      {% if program.featured %}
      <article class="program-card" data-aos="fade-up">
        <a href="{{ ('/' + program.slug + '/') | url }}">
          <div class="program-card-image">
            <img src="/assets/images/programs/{{ program.id }}-card.jpg" alt="{{ program.name }}" loading="lazy">
            <div class="program-card-overlay">
              <span class="program-age-range">{{ program.ageRange }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="program-card-content">
            <h3 class="program-card-title">{{ program.name }}</h3>
            <p class="program-card-description">{{ program.shortDescription }}</p>
            <span class="program-card-link">Conocer más →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2 class="cta-title">Únete al universo vaemptîness</h2>
      <p class="cta-description">Pulsa para volver a tí.</p>
      <a href="{{ '/contacto/' | url }}" class="button button-primary">Cuestiónate y calma</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

